data.description: Move right in! This modern 3 bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom home boasts so many updates throughout! Upon entering, you're greeted by a perfect open floor plan that seamlessly combines the living, dining, and kitchen area. The space is flooded with natural light streaming through large windows, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Kitchen is complete with newer cabinets, countertops, SS appliances and fixtures! Newer flooring throughout - along with fresh paint and trim.  First floor owners suite including full bathroom and walk in closet! Upstairs are two more spacious bedrooms. Every bathroom has been beautifully updated. Lower level includes an additional living space with half bathroom and LL laundry. Large fenced in backyard. 2 car attached garage. HVAC replaced in 2023.
